</span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-246_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d5abed07-e7b5-41b8-9cb6-69f9a515a007"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">It allows organisations to:
